Family system: You are born in any random family
Stat system: rolling stats like in DnD (max 3 rolls) previous stats get overwritten
Race system: Based on your race, your stats get boosted
Weapon system: Add more variety of weaopns and classes
Quest system: Able to accept quests and gain karma
NPC system: Various npc's with different karma, reputation system (get discounts, add in party)
